{
  "title": "Catalog of Mech Blocks",
  "story": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "2802ed0bdf73bd98",
      "text": "Each block is a capitalized word that leads to specific computations. Blocks use and update state passed from block to block. They can reach into the federated wiki client and server-side environment. Expect them to offer informative messages as they run."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "ae5a798937198031",
      "text": "# Client"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "f7a7b0a6589250e2",
      "text": "[[CLICK]] — Offer to proceed once user clicks."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "becdc6dd737d7f6a",
      "text": "[[DELTA]] — Apply recent remote site changes."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "e5dbc564e1d54a41",
      "text": "[[FILE]] — User selects one of avalable files."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "1033f16d3f024a47",
      "text": "[[FORWARD]] — Move the drawing \"turtle\" forward."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "abc462d385a0459f",
      "text": "[[FROM]] — Read sensor endpoints from a page."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "e78c3e43a0e8d97a",
      "text": "[[GET]] — Await a result from the server."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "d2ebf84d1e3bddfb",
      "text": "[[HELLO]] — Add a happy face each time run."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "52d4f2dc1a544d95",
      "text": "[[KWIC]] — Costruct a Keword-In-Context index."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "e28130e126f1618a",
      "text": "[[LINEUP]] — Make a page from current lineup."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "081c2a7d3832f64d",
      "text": "[[LISTEN]] — Wait for a specific message."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "8c153cbacbc5990d",
      "text": "[[MESSAGE]] — Send a specific message."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "f57a2887eac58cbd",
      "text": "[[NEIGHBORS]] — Retrieve avalable neighborhood sitemaps."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "acf7d4c9441658f3",
      "text": "[[PREVIEW]] — Display computed state as a ghost page."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "5ad261075a1c1ee1",
      "text": "[[RANDOM]] — Select a random page from the neighbors."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "16c8189aff87fab0",
      "text": "[[REPORT]] — Report measurement in place in the item."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "3718566dc9b0a107",
      "text": "[[ROSTER]] — Make a Roster for current neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "2089a42393098a3d",
      "text": "[[SENSOR]] — Read sensor data from a named endpoint."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "1580d5c85aefaaee",
      "text": "[[SHOW]] — Add an existing page to the lineup."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "f23b1693cb1935cf",
      "text": "[[SLEEP]] — Suspend a sequence of blocks."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "a511c33dcf6fd1e3",
      "text": "[[SOLO]] — Launch the Solo plugins pop-up viewer."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "2ef27430b137893d",
      "text": "[[SOURCE]] — Read a data source from the lineup."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "a6ee0eab87f3e07d",
      "text": "[[TICK]] — Proceed repeatedly once user clicks."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "be36918c1678f34a",
      "text": "[[TOGETHER]] — Start all blocks at once."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "b5bcaa7faf914468",
      "text": "[[TURN]] — Turn the drawing \"turtle\" to a new direction."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "8b08d40b0c9bbb1e",
      "text": "[[UNTIL]] — Stop TICKing one a condition is met."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "3eb205fc672ddb84",
      "text": "[[WALK]] ` Explore the neighborhood link graph."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "caadee975b92db5c",
      "text": "[[POPUP]] — Open a pop-up window with various contents."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "12d8c48fc2f901ff",
      "text": "# Server "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "3253e8bfb73b4f5c",
      "text": "[[HELLO]] — Add a happy face each time run."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "26acbfadb4eb7af3",
      "text": "[[UPTIME]] — Report time server has run."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "d073181d1c732b21",
      "text": "[[SLEEP]] — Suspend a sequence of blocks."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "84a76e762f9b9bce",
      "text": "[[COMMONS]] — Report image file and byte count."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "9334b669ce1b2215",
      "text": "[[DELTA]] — Retrieve recent site chages."
    }
  ],
